  "page": "Archon's daughter (Jaehaerys I)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Not to be confused with <a href=\"/index.php/Archon%27s_green-haired_daughter\" title=\"Archon&#39;s green-haired daughter\">Archon's green-haired daughter</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\"><img alt=\"Tyrosh.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/50px-Tyrosh.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/75px-Tyrosh.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d7/Tyrosh.svg/100px-Tyrosh.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Archon's daughter</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\"><img alt=\"House Baratheon.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/50px-House_Baratheon.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/75px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2d/House_Baratheon.svg/100px-House_Baratheon.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Archon&#39;s Daughter by gothgleek.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg/350px-Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/61/Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg/525px-Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/61/Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg/700px-Archon%27s_Daughter_by_gothgleek.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>The Archon's daughter, by gothgleek ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon\" title=\"House Baratheon\">House Baratheon</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyroshi</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_34_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">34&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nSer <a href=\"/index.php/Orryn_Baratheon\" title=\"Orryn Baratheon\">Orryn Baratheon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\nDaughter</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> <small>(mentioned)</small></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Archon's daughter</b> was the daughter of the <a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> She was the wife of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Orryn_Baratheon\" title=\"Orryn Baratheon\">Orryn Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Her given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Archon%27s_daughter_(Jaehaerys_I)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Archon%27s_daughter_(Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Category:Images of Archon&#39;s daughter (Jaehaerys I)\">Images of Archon's daughter</a></div>\n<p>The Archon's daughter was comely and buxom. She <a href=\"/index.php/Hair_dye\" title=\"Hair dye\">dyed</a> her hair blue-green and wore it in long tresses. She was witty and liked to flirt, and had a \"<a href=\"/index.php/Tyroshi_language\" title=\"Tyroshi language\">delightful accent</a>\" when speaking the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Archon%27s_daughter_(Jaehaerys_I)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>In <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maiden</a> came to <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> at the age of fifteen with her father, the <a href=\"/index.php/Archon_of_Tyrosh\" title=\"Archon of Tyrosh\">Archon of Tyrosh</a>, to attend the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a>. After the wedding, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> proposed to the other members of King <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Small_council\" title=\"Small council\">small council</a> that she wed the young king, in order to forge an alliance with <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> and extend the power of the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. However, <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Regent\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen Regent\">Queen Regent</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> argued that the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> would never accept a foreign woman with dyed hair as their queen. She felt a Tyroshi, who kept foreign <a href=\"/index.php/Gods\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Gods\">gods</a>, would also be strongly opposed by those pious to the <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">Faith of the Seven</a>. She had her own ideal candidates for Jaehaerys's bride, which other council members opposed, proposing their own suggestions as they argued for a month without reaching a consensus.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/50_AC\" title=\"50 AC\">50&#160;AC</a>, King Jaehaerys sentenced Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Orryn_Baratheon\" title=\"Orryn Baratheon\">Orryn Baratheon</a> to a ten-year exile for attempting to kidnap Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen_(daughter_of_Aegon)\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen (daughter of Aegon)\">Rhaella Targaryen</a>. Orryn entered the service of the Archon in Tyrosh, and the following year he married the Archon's daughter. She soon gave birth to a girl, although some doubted that Orryn was the father.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Archon%27s_daughter_(Jaehaerys_I)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Archon.27s_daughter_.28Jaehaerys_I.29\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Archon's daughter (Jaehaerys I)</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Year of the Three Brides - 49 AC.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfaba_time_of_testing_-_the_realm_remade.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, A Time of Testing - The Realm Remade.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403194438\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.088 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.292 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 916/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10760/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8851/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1668/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2648/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.82 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  277.645      1 -total\n 75.52%  209.666      1 Template:Infobox_chara